    • setFrictionsAreaType

      public void setFrictionsAreaType(String className, double kinetic_friction, double static_friction)
      Sets the kinetic and static frictions for the specified AreaType object. If the object is an instance of Grass or Sand, their respective friction values are updated accordingly.
      Parameters:
      className - The AreaType object for which frictions need to be set.
      kinetic_friction - The new kinetic friction value.
      static_friction - The new static friction value.
